   @{b}@{i}@{fg shine}AAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAGGGGGGGGGGGGGGGGGGHHHHHH!!!!!!!!!!!!!!@{ub}@{ui}@{fg text}


      As mentioned elsewhere this is a beta-test version of the game. There
are several bugs I am aware of.

      The most serious one involves the colors. For some reason I can`t
figure out the game does not load the full palette. Whether this is down to
a fault in Blitz Basic 2 or due to my inept programming I don`t know. If
anyone knows of a solution to this problem please write.
      The temporary solution to this problem is that I`ve put a title screen
at the beginning which uses the same palette and used viewtek to load it up
thus loading the higher color registers with the apropriate colors.
Inelegant but what else can I do. If you know how to fix this bug from
inside Blitz2 I`d be grateful if you could write.
      Other bugs involve minor colision detection problems which I`m working
on.
      If any bugs irritate you a great deal please @{"write and complain" link "author" 0}.
@endnode

